PrecisOrder authorizing the trip undertaken by Senator Gerald A. Ottenheimer, George S. Baker, M.P., Peter L. McCreath, M.P., and David Stupich, M.P., to several European countries from May 25 to June 1, 1992, as part of a Joint Parliamentary, Industry and Union Delegation whose purpose was to address audiences in the European Community on the question of foreign overfishing in the North Atlantic.
